      "title": "Ranjan\u2019s Pardon: Documents sent to President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Minister of Justice, Dr. Wijayadasa Rajapaksa PC says that all the documents relating to granting the Presidential pardon to former MP Ranjan Ramanayake have been forwarded to the President.",
        "The minister said that the relevant documents were forwarded to President Ranil Wickramasinghe last week.",
        "QR system in effect from 1st August : 12 important points to know before heading to pump fuel"
